item.title: Wtf!
item.dc:creator: @ninja_nub ninja nub
item.description:
@ninja_nub wrote:

Um…Same happened to me. I think its your firewall…Go to Norton > Norton Internet Security > Settings > Scroll down to Internet Security and Firewall Options > Advanced Settings > Configure > Add > and fill out the Information Needed.

Hope I helped :D[br][size=1]Posted on: September 16, 2007, 08:22:49 AM[/size][hr]BTW - Thats if you have norton. But other programs should be generaly similar.
